name: separatechainsofblocksrunningtogethercreatingpatternsatintersections
description: Different blockchains working together in harmony. Every block moves the adjacent block, creating a chain reaction in its own color grid. Various patterns emerge at their intersections. This piece is created for @WorldArtDay2021 #WorldArtDay2021 #NFTsForAll #CleanNFTs #NFTs
